# Design System — Faith Generation App

## Design Philosophy

Matches [faithgeneration.com](https://faithgeneration.com/): **minimal black, white, and grey**. No accent colors except red for errors and green for success/streaks.

- Minimal — black, white, grey palette
- High contrast — clear typography hierarchy
- Professional — aligned with the ministry's website

## useTheme Hook (always use this)

```typescript
import { useTheme } from '@/hooks/useTheme';

function MyComponent() {
  const theme = useTheme();
  // Use theme.* tokens everywhere — never hardcode hex values
}
```

## Complete ThemeColors Interface

Every token available on the `theme` object:

```typescript
interface ThemeColors {
  // Backgrounds
  pageBg: string;           // Page/screen background
  cardBg: string;           // Card surface
  emptyBg: string;          // Empty state background
  messageBg: string;        // Message/notification background
  inputBg: string;          // Input field background
  overlayBg: string;        // Semi-transparent overlay (modal backdrop)

  // Borders
  cardBorder: string;       // Card borders, dividers

  // Text
  textPrimary: string;      // Headings, primary content
  textSecondary: string;    // Body text, labels
  textTertiary: string;     // Placeholders, muted/helper text

  // Buttons
  buttonPrimary: string;    // Primary CTA background
  buttonPrimaryContrast: string; // Text ON primary buttons (not white/black — use this)
  buttonAccept: string;     // Accept/confirm action
  buttonDecline: string;    // Decline/destructive action
  buttonDeclineContrast: string; // Text on decline buttons

  // Brand
  brandAccent: string;      // Brand accent (same as buttonPrimary)
  brandAccentMuted: string; // Muted brand accent (semi-transparent)

  // Tab bar
  tabActive: string;        // Active tab indicator/icon
  tabInactiveBg: string;    // Inactive tab background
  tabInactiveText: string;  // Inactive tab label color

  // Avatars & icons
  avatarPrimary: string;    // Default avatar/icon background
  avatarWarning: string;    // Warning-state avatar background

  // Badges (background colors)
  badgeSuccess: string;     // Success badge bg
  badgeError: string;       // Error badge bg
  badgeWarning: string;     // Warning badge bg
  badgeInfo: string;        // Info badge bg
  badgeSuccessBg: string;   // Translucent success bg (rgba)
  badgeInfoBg: string;      // Translucent info bg (rgba)

  // Quiz feedback
  quizCorrect: string;      // Correct answer text color
  quizCorrectBg: string;    // Correct answer background
  quizIncorrect: string;    // Incorrect answer text color
  quizIncorrectBg: string;  // Incorrect answer background

  // Special
  starSuccess: string;      // Star/streak icon color
  isDark: boolean;          // True when dark mode is active
}
```

